# Project-specific
# Ignore every file under data/ except the committed demo DB used by the
# Streamlit dashboard deploy. We split the rule instead of using `data/`
# wholesale because git doesn't descend into a directory blocked by a
# trailing-slash pattern, even when a re-include follows.
data/*
briefs/*.md
!briefs/example_*.md
eval_reports/*.html
*.db
*.db-journal
# Re-include the demo DB LAST so it overrides both `data/*` and `*.db`.
!data/episodic.demo.db
